title: Dans la peau de Jean-Claude Van Damme

sources.title: Van Damme - Black Eagle 1988 - There are no enemies. There is no glory. This fight is one on one. 4K
sources.description:
A CIA free-lancer (Shô Kosugi) takes his children and a baby sitter (Doran Clark) to Malta, where he meets his KGB match (Jean-Claude Van Damme).

Original title: Black Eagle (1988)

Director: Eric Karson
Writers: Michael Gonzales, A. E. Peters

Main cast:
Shō Kosugi - Ken Tani
Jean-Claude Van Damme - Andrei
Doran Clark - Patricia Parker
Vladimir Skomarovsky - Captain Nikolaiev
Kane Kosugi - Brian Tani

Genres: Action, Martial Arts
Release date: May 19, 1988
Filming location: Malta
